                            <comment id="16478" author="alef.arendsen" created="Fri, 17 Feb 2006 08:48:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;First up: an element for the SimpleUrlHandlerMapping&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16652" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Fri, 3 Mar 2006 11:24:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;To be revisited for 2.0 RC1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="24514" author="grant.gochnauer" created="Mon, 25 Jun 2007 05:10:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Juergen,&lt;br/&gt;
Any reason this was dropped from 2.1?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="24516" author="springboy" created="Mon, 25 Jun 2007 09:01:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Grant&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(Copying text from &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-2764&quot; title=&quot;configuring a SimpleUrlHandlerMapping through a schema&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPR-2764&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPR-2764&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After some discussion internally it has been decided to &apos;shelve&apos; the MVC-specific tags indefinitely (or until enough folks in the community vote on this issue). The reason for shelving this issue (for now) is that there doesn&apos;t seem to be enough &apos;value-add&apos; provided by these new tags to warrant doing them, simple as that.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cheers&lt;br/&gt;
Rick&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="24517" author="grant.gochnauer" created="Mon, 25 Jun 2007 09:19:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks Rick for the update.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;-Grant&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="47036" author="youngm" created="Mon, 28 Sep 2009 15:02:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I hope this makes it in to rc2.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;One feature I hope will make it into the handler is the ability to set in one place &quot;alwaysUseFullPath&quot;.  In my project the way that I manage my servlet mappings I have to add the following:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;	&amp;lt;bean class=&quot;org.springframework.web.servlet.mvc.annotation.DefaultAnnotationHandlerMapping&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
		&amp;lt;property name=&quot;alwaysUseFullPath&quot; value=&quot;true&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
	&amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;	&amp;lt;bean class=&quot;org.springframework.web.servlet.mvc.annotation.AnnotationMethodHandlerAdapter&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
		&amp;lt;property name=&quot;alwaysUseFullPath&quot; value=&quot;true&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
	&amp;lt;/bean&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It would be nice to simply make &quot;always-use-full-path&quot; a single default attribute for the default Handlers.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
